Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:39.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've waited and waited,\nbut she hasn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, let her have it\nher way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:46.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you bums!\NWe're heading home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:48.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Back to Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:54.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All I could do was\nstand there and stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:59.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At the now masterless\nnumber 30, Champs Elysées.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:05.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At the city blocks that had crumbled away\nlike sandcastles built on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:09.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At the silent blue sky\nthat spread out above me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:15.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The summer storm\nhad come and gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:20.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the end\nof our summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.98,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,352)}Final Act:\NAt the Shore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:35.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\bord0\shad2\4c&H514B35&\pos(352,321)\c&HFDFBFB&}Five Years Later
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:15.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, if it isn't the\ngood Chief Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:19.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, the Assistant Editor-in-Chief\ncame in person, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a hard worker\nyou are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:24.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was just worried about whether or not\nyou're carrying out your duties properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:27.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, how's the peace treaty\ncoming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:30.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Treaty Nearing Finalization At Long Last."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something along\nthose lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:37.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this treaty, the restoration of\ndiplomatic relations between our Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:41.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and the Empire is finally starting\nto look like a real possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:45.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, this marathon of a war\nis finally gonna end, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Civilian interaction will\nbecome commonplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and citizens of both nations will\ntake each other by the hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:56.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see the birth of a nation that's prosperous\nin the truest sense of the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:05:00.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not a nation where only\na select few prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:01.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:06.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling when\nthe times will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:11.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I want to\nbelieve in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:15.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe in the people\nwho chose THIS solution at THIS time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:18.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And that includes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:21.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Me, I just go with the flow\nwith those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:25.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's leave the question of the truth\nof that statement for another time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day of our long-awaited reunion\nwith those dear old friends of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:31.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:32.82,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:37.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you forgot\nto make reservations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:40.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Tell my secretary that I'll be late\nfor the afternoon Cabinet meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And tell her you're out making a reservation\nso important that you can't trust her to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:48.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See you tonight at the Nouveau Casino!\NWe'll start off with a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:55.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, I came all the way down here\nto show him this article...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(442,153,448,145)\frz-20.5\frx7\c&H515050&\bord2\b1\3c&HE8E5E6&}Claire-Marie Eugenie's\NTriumphant Return to Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Julie! Julie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Uncle Maximilien!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me the "uncle" bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:32.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother! Thank goodness you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:36.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you behave yourselves and\ndo what Emmanuel told you to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:43.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. I have presents waiting\nfor children who behaved themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:44.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Uncle Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:47.38,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:48.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.63,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maximilien!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maximilien!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:36.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've returned, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:41.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The peace that you dreamed of for so long\nbetween Earth and the Empire...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is finally about\nto come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:49.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, I resigned from\nthe military as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:56.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The flow of goods traveling between Earth\nand the Empire will grow and grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:59.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So I intend to buy back my\nfather's ship, the Pharaon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and help Emmanuel and Julie\nwith the family business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maximilien...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:13.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Maximilien!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't get moving soon,\nwe'll be late for the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have an eye\nfor quality, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:49.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's an import item.\NAll the way from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a brand that's famous\nin Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:56.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would it look good\non black hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:03.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These models from Earth certainly\nare pretty, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:09.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say that it goes perfectly with black hair,\nwouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:10.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Peppo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.\NI'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:16.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...? But sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:22.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Trinkets like that aren't good enough\nfor our Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:27.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It will be a whole\nnew you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you care to\njoin me, Bertuccio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:57.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, ma'am. I'm on guard duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:02.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to\nshow you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:12.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It says that Monsieur Albert will be arriving\nhere on the day of the coronation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:16.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And that he will do so as a secretarial aide\nto Earth's ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:23.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bertuccio, what would you\ncall this, if not fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:28.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our old master must have\nguided him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:32.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that you would be able to fulfill your duties\nto the best of your ability, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:41.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:50.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I also wish to keep Janina safe, so that\nthis peace endures for years to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:55.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That desire will\nnever change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And we will be there\nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:03.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Bertuccio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:21.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Air France flight 1027 from Galileo\nto Paris Spaceport...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...will be entering Earth\norbit momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:28.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our estimated arrival time in Paris\nwill be slightly behind schedule,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...which will now be 2:13 local time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:31.72,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A search is underway for the two ringleaders,\NBenedetto and Gaspard Caderousse,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...who are wanted fugitives\nin all systems, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In Paris, it's 2 o'clock, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:22.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done paying\nyour respects, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:28.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Time certainly flies,\ndoesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:33.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How many times will I have\nheard you play now? Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:40.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you manage to meet your\nfriend this year? Your... young gentleman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:53.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Father. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:13.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there, Franz.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:28.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As I said when we spoke over the phone,\NI simply wasn't able to find a buyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:34.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As such, we will be taking the house to pay for\nthe five years of accumulated back taxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:39.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um..."The state hereby assumes all legal rights\nto this land and all structures thereupon,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"...and will take over management\nof said land and structures."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure that's\nall right with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:46.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. I have\nno objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, please sign\nthis form.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:59.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Would it be all right if I went\ninto the mansion one last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:03.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Feel free to\ngo in while you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:05.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've been frantic\nthese past five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:52.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I read books like crazy,\nalways hunched over my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And before I knew it, I'd turned 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:59.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was... I was simply frantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told myself that I had to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:08.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That I had to live in your place, in Father's\nplace, and in the Count's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:16.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz, I was terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:19.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of being trapped\nby the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:25.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That I might become obsessed with the past\nand end up hating someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Franz...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:38.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry it's been so long.\NI'm sorry I haven't come back for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:48.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mademoiselle Mercedes Herrera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:52.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a long time.\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:55.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The ship has finally begun\nher return voyage to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:18:00.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, the Captain\nhas fallen ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:05.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that it is anything serious, but\nit looks as if our return will be delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:10.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I wish I could come home\nright now and hold you in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That day we set sail,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:16.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I could see the lights of Marseilles from the\nporthole as they receded into the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:23.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A day doesn't go by when I don't think back\non that warm light, the light of my loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:29.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Guided by that light, I never lose my way\nor stray from my path.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:35.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That light that is shining so brightly\nin our future is happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:40.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So please wait for me\nand don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:46.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of holding you in my arms now,\nI offer you these words:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:51.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bide your time,\nand hold out hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:54.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To my beloved Mercedes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:19:00.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With all my heart,\nyour Edmond Dantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:15.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've been here all this time...\NSince long before I was born, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:29.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget the time I spent with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or the time I spent\nwith my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or the time I spent\nwith the Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:39.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I swear this\nto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:47.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where my life takes me,\NI'll never forget that summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:49.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Never.
